\v 40 I…ôrmama riti nemh…ôien skai riti ram…ômak ia tek…®n. In ruvehe t…® Iesu, m…®n…®mwi nukurhun mi ia n…ônimen, m…®ni pen tukwe in m…ô, ‚ÄúM…ô rer…®m ra…°ien ko iko iak…ômher?‚Äù
