\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Aes 43:25, 1Jon 1:9\x*‚ÄúR…ôfo i…ôm…ô n…ôha ram…ô…°kiari iam…®nha ir…ô m…®ne? N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha r…ôr…ôha. Kumwes…ôn …ôpa rukur…ôn nenouenouien noien …ôr…ôha me. Sin mwi rukur…ôn noien?‚Äù
