\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Mat 11:19, Luk 15:1-2\x*N…ôn…ô nahat…ôn me s…ôv…ôi Loa, ir…ôha mwi Farisi me, h…ôuvehe mh…ôtoni Iesu ram…ôni nari ir…ôha n…ôrmama kam…ôr…ôku pen takis m…®nraha m…®ne n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me nepw…®n mwi. Ir…ôha h…ôres n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi m…ô, ‚ÄúR…ôfo in ram…ôni nari ir…ôha n…ôrmama kam…ôr…ôku pen takis m…®nraha m…®ne n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me nepw…®n mwi?‚Äù
