\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Mat 22:15-16\x*N…ôn…ô Farisi me h…ôier irapw, mh…ôuv…ôn akwauakw t…® n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Ki…° Herot. Ir…ôha hous…ôs…®mw…®n ir…ôha me mh…ôni …ôr…ôha Iesu, mamh…ôtui suatuk m…ô tuhousi …ôpune in.
