\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Mak 3:7-9, Luk 5:1-3\x*Iesu r…®namahat…ôn mwi n…ôrmama ia n…®kare nui asori. N…ôrmama me h…ôp…®k h…ôuvehe mhous…ôs…®mw…®n pen ir…ôha me tukwe. Ro pen Iesu r…ôput…ô ia n…®t…ôt…ô ouihi riti fwe peraha, m…ôkure ir…ô. N…ôrmama me pam kamh…ôrer parei ia n…®kare nui asori.
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Mat 13:34, Mak 4:33-34\x*Iesu ramahat…ôn ir…ôha narimnari me r…®p…®k ia nusipek…®nien me. N…ôp…®n ramahat…ôn ir…ôha, rani m…ô,
\v 3 ‚ÄúTih…ôre…°i ro! I…ôrmama riti rev…ôn m…ô truini nuni nari ia n…ômhien s…ôv…ônhi.
