\v 6 Nuanraha rouihi. Ro pen n…ôp…®n meri r…ôkwiri, m…ônhi, haukei pam.
\v 7 Nuni nari me nepw…®n h…ôsas pen ia t…®pr…ôn…ô s…ô n…ôkwus …ôr…ôha raut…ô ir…ô. N…ôkwus …ôr…ôha me n…ôha h…ôuvir…®s mh…ôuvehe mhous…ôman pam. Ro pen nuni nari me h…ôpkuku…ô mh…ô.
\v 8 Nuni nari me nepw…®n h…ôsas pen ia t…®pr…ôn…ô amasan, mh…ôut…ô amasan, mh…ôuku…ô. Nepw…®n kw…ônkwan toti, nepw…®n kw…ônkwan sikisti, nepw…®n kw…ônkwan hantret.‚Äù
