\v 11 Iesu r…®ni pen t…® nir…ôha i m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôiou k…®n…ôsev…ôr ia suatuk tukumiaha hi…ôukur…ôn n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô m…ô in r…ôfo ir…ô. M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama iru…ô me, iakamahat…ôn ir…ôha ia nusipek…®nien me a,
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Jon 12:40, Wok Me 28:26-27\x*m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôt…ô, m…ôt…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôien mh…ôukur…ôn. Ir…ôha tuh…ôre…°i, m…ôt…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh n…®re…°iien mh…ôukur…ôn. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô ko ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh n…®r…ôr…®…°ien mh…ôuvehe t…® Kumwes…ôn m…®nu…ô in trenouenou noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha.‚Äù
\s1 Iesu r…®ni irapw n…®pwrai nusipek…®nien
