\v 21 \fig Kolkota|alt="Gol…°atha" src="HK00323B.TIF" size="col" loc="Mark 15:21" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="Mak 15:21"\fig*\x - \xo 15:21 \xt Rom 16:13\x*Ir…ôha h…ôiri Iesu, mamh…ôuv…ôn. Ia suatuk narua…°…ôn me h…ôtoni i…ôm…ô Saerin riti. N…ô…°h…®n n…ô Saemon. In tata s…ôv…ôi Aleksanta m…®ne Rufas. Ruku pen fwe ia rukw…ônu mauvehe i ia taon. Narua…°…ôn me h…ôkeikei min m…ô tr…ôvrani nei kamarkuaui s…ôv…ôi Iesu.
