\v 1 R…®nam…ôruar…ôv, n…ôp…®n Sapat r…®no sampam, Meri Maktala, m…®ne Salome, m…®ne Meri mama s…ôv…ôi Jemes, haruvehi n…ômri n…®mwai nari me nepw…®n s…ô n…®pek…®nraha rapein amasan, m…ô tuharev…ôn mhar…ômri pen ia n…®pwrai Iesu.
