\v 6 M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama n…ôha r…®ni pen t…® nir…ôhar i m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ômr…®mir…ôhar tr…ôpw…ôh nierien. Hiamar…ôtui Iesu, i…ôm…ô Nasaret s…ô k…®n…ôrui t…ôrini pen ia nei kamarkuaui. In riw…ôn i. R…®n…ôtui raka ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi. Har…ôtoni ro kwopun k…®n…ômri pen n…®pwran ram…ômak ik…®n.
\v 7 \x - \xo 16:7 \xt Mat 26:32, Mak 14:28\x*M…ôt…ô tiharev…ôn mharni pen t…® n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne Pita m…ô Iesu trukupw…ôn ia k…®miaha mamev…ôn fwe ia t…ôn…ô Kalili. K…®miaha tih…ôtoni in fwe ik…®n r…ômwhen r…®m…ôni tukumiaha i.‚Äù
