\v 8 N…ôn…ô n…®pr…ôn mir…ôhar n…ôha harhek…®r p…®k, mhar…ôt…ômn…®mw…®n, mharier, mharap ia n…®p…ô…°. M…ôt…ô har…ôpw…ôh n…ôvisauien n…ôfe k…®m…ôni pen t…® nir…ôhar i, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô harhek…®r.
